.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkKDIRucaP5DRL6WWdaAYm4mUl2y8-SK4kob9O0U83ixPoUwpxPKSRiCMzqTu8LwKmUjUmCdCHoZfS4AaLT9pHFB1SBxdx_eJkjX0GOVTxhHhLkiUuV2HWSJiWmvvepY9GFnQ1RXgDtDB1qwmWArV5X0FsKbMFPXRogoiZ1V8lo5EzxOg0FPRjJqIxMfXMFR3Y2imkYXakptzLWuolBG3wEq7ywQUrEIAwWLK1X2RnBlkIpmOTRguy6HQLWMptbOO_GTd0cGVecApzqsXjsj7mbE-LVEKtOFyyFrtAfjbqv_X8HEjRT9iPQgy9hjUX6rkiA%3D%3D" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099799&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li=12319720&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=01152025" style="width: 108px !important; display: block;" width="108" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;周三的新数据显示，美国通胀再次放缓，引发股市上涨和债券收益率暴跌，因为投资者（其中一些人几天前还认为美联储不会很快降息） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkEvJi24-Np-3QapZzHGEw-Vhxxx8whkpiEtONwy8uUYsK-3sfgwZ0cJPJ6O-XfpWbT-hvZ6GX0R_DqDVOQCVZiYlCTmUU-PIKmZ9x6BD0o-zZM-fWIVifTTAzFVqLfmkDORFhMHZwCN4KDh9AkyJarMjgMdxopX-xrLW53PwzLU8fv4JOSm5KKHDsnKfRg7RmNDXXhxTjTqHt-WYRD_BZ4-BSHqPR2Du6lpRnh1yaSTNDNev_fBXlKL0nc3FnsBQK7DlLLja93PA8vgUfFgN8fxarhJ8oXTbfTbgHwEK_mCe3el_eKv58MuuFulPXt0nEg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;再次充满希望&lt;/a&gt;。股市在新的一年里抹去了损失，标准普尔 500 指数上涨了约 2%，这是自&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkFmdCZImuTtKH8oqDCKpOFvnS_2CJyLjVUe4bvDZG-2Uz3eOlrEF0cxMXvNTIAsYUsisIWf8t0dwgF9sGLTN1GVOBAN8jiRiJMuWDqyuq5dfH_l2Yvnd_p1Qk9Qt2uaE6YTchBwA9b8y6gNIiIqMDQ6zmskCYdNg7AMKFygI1j9z9PzN5rS9VADLg1TKW-lhbD3NqFnIQn5KPaYBwx3rm6GmMz4JJ7_1FLJmjVrFCfyKjd4LNuwsxumNkVn775ELU_kJJ7hOIMImlGy6rkN2Sy2xJwyNkSQPdUxSJ8IL9gBr35xSVh3vSoBAo3CNCUXH5Q%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;美国大选&lt;/a&gt;以来的最大涨幅。国债飙升将 10 年期国债收益率推低近 15 个基点，缓解了人们对 5% 利率水平的担忧。大宗商品价格飙升，油价突破每桶 80 美元。彭博社汇编的数据显示，跨资产的一致上涨是至少自 2023 年末以来消费者价格指数日的最佳表现。 Evercore的克里希纳·古哈(Krishna Guha)表示，消费者物价指数(CPI)报告增强了这样一种论点，即市场已经“过度交易”通胀故事，不应再如此&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkNrjVtIr42JCcGGoQL5e4XJskvJwKG95MdkZBc3EFRl7jAridnkuHzYyfGhKe09GhoGQ9exwqpyGnsuu39AvieoZ-yJX5Wnpt8sDj0XZb_3SUNURaf6Y-PPDEKAahURVP2p4WstIvg2aPX3DLmCMhZVCGAs96LqYCjhKLZI8df7IERVIkXMML-4XeRkcQuTaTNV9xCFxw5dBQBw51BNbNNpjGrj733PEjINoH2oQm0u7D0odh-qtrzeRoQjVibM7qXGv0l2_3svqKwCqaGknUEqLSLK9xb3KC8BGqqybDDlF9Ix9AFLs_FGfEv4iC-LbDw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;厌恶风险&lt;/a&gt;。他表示：“这强化了美联储两次降息的基本情况，并保持了三月份降息的可能性。” &lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;— &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkE2mMJgSZbgqhqbaDPckjNkJ5qP77lzkAwjoFUPqYYiMn7vBptkuRPg-wQzjFpxYqZEEHUQh2cyFi9nZBMTpqnfpY94x_9dQ5KCy6Z09i5V0j_RwJqILIiM4gyjhr9OV9aS-ksifvdCoayCU3Zpvy-BsXdd50iDJdQ8yOcqJuElPVP-wyYEOHv0tPZiaNOSdCqKcS4Yny1XRF7-l7b6kx-Ilm4TC76jlpZrLsOZwV_9cZsG4VA4GXK5kDAJY0DYSumwG_KB1-osE0rfoEJlYVLraNL59ZzyXbDOuSYCOYkl6Iwxq27hHX_WfpYUjGwiUMg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;大卫·E·罗维拉&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;本周有报道&lt;/strong&gt;称加沙即将达成协议，事实证明，以色列和哈马斯周三&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkAaYFUS_aUNCXOgPhgYRSKKWm6OJmcTYkCl9dywL05hUcikj602SldU3RidRJAgZrm9TTKJZUyQIERZiqHue6-ZrGeYKpcwUMtRqhd14sops8UdfowyJLiA6B0XbAOvMKP5WUml8SIQfrQDy9EFwv7ytUxXPsX8S4lZwhgeL2VfvsxovC8GtEvTiAAjwvI7GcNSgRNwsrMVuw3Z3uPx4Qa7Q67qiGSuFARoPNACwqqODspmNxiorH-ixHV2fSGlz2vZyR-gKWx1yu4f0kBR0qlYIkn3SgLg1SWjNoycA8ae01xkBNoYpJb7DGWHFN5iXYQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;同意达成停火协议&lt;/a&gt;，该协议将释放数十名人质，并暂时停止长达 15 个月的战争。卡塔尔和美国官员表示，停火将于周日（唐纳德·特朗普就职前一天）开始，持续六周。 2023 年 10 月哈马斯袭击以色列后被俘的 33 名人质将被释放，以色列将从&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkOlI6zs-lOTI6CfwsZf2Cz1BVA1zBc4bL4C_oC4zQq3lwtxUCp3Ry7T-kL32GRSaefBlLpU7V6nAb71LYLPlAWUhAoxwmyUW2yu4PC1EGexzw5wiHalubYnkwmBkj2flHFu4Q-Py5KpD-xsDl-sCRwd1UvKu7lO_Wn91x_gDNSrc5gMjnYuGNezu3q5YZLOnIygpYvCdx1_-8bD7KqYBsrM9USH_FwpWau7m5pc-0QDOmISkyZmz-lDBJb0XdIy3rMc2e_xXAew3rUCy2y8G1IsbmfLKYcRsoNrrLcAAKs1IyLuW-JCwcyGzHGmJvAxvSg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;加沙地带人口稠密地区&lt;/a&gt;撤军，并释放数百名巴勒斯坦囚犯。尽管美国总统乔·拜登称赞该协议最初是由其政府制定的，也是白宫（以及当选总统唐纳德·特朗普最近的顾问）“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkJRp4qhm54lsEjPjloKTrsJ7_moqZO7ZYLWUIu7Udz4t_W9IbuGoqbAHI3BVBhajC9E_xwbGANSF-gzmAyZczhwuexYj0SUHvADH30v6oayPxxtXo6sTESQei2YKgJIPTBhhe6LoY-A9ThRjF6Gk4-CZiK1HRMsPx7suSvBV4GFGc3p6WLhnnxYkSwjOR3i3rbAbUaeGTmwWuoxx3EtKbfh5BMMS9dW-clYNcjk7dFaELdYNoZbzFA_ZUxP8mtirJ-0SAc8bOdSPNcM-lIQsDTltHnrY5jXfuzUDsIAitikS9PFZCgSFb6DYZEe1_dU5BWtwsubzw0hgUu3ZYFRIPpVuplLOTR3mfmWyD8o1-Bv0FM0-jRycTOrzb-eMAkIkkdGbm4ebIvlLgjGIZPIKpVXsRxeYHVCR5o9k4gwMRRzmZVKHXgMtlJzMnwPeAf0wyRgR3S7PPIXH1IwCack6k_9Sq5P2RBZPfNlwahfkVU6GB1fi5H4k8x6tvBkedskMAw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;艰苦&lt;/a&gt;”谈判的结果，但以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的办公室表示仍有一些细节需要解决，交易尚未最终确定。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkIY1rT0WDMPUr8yRUKLEfXxMCRaM6p-XD0lzbMuei9aQ7wm52INRlhS2Ea86-6odMrLiOeZWd3muLrYYQhvde0o99Dq2Kd9V6Ez5DZCMsSvmgzclqOIqElI9yX64TQb4lBxSrAZJuNjd6ajQiyzy3NDltFfGbjCZ75gDoL6C7ZWBp4lL6NvzyuOKS75ADIbAc_RMfJGx3KKQSNF7MKnmB0KySHRRMa5iY1AdkByu4Dcm_lN7Cw4RZ2dqhJnNJA_qmLmpouofSyJP0xLpaRHsT-pa9-vS0BGTqyXmTdbIJJiWojoIuRrUmr3jWxkC-1VqoA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;接下来可能会发生以下&lt;/a&gt;情况。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkAaYFUS_aUNCXOgPhgYRSKJkGISyjNw5jjvg4zqT_rAUWQm5zw3u5_qgGMnnXUNJ6WOWV_AjcWDyN4HobrGb83o7zWpgCFMoMUYufykKntjsHz7GYOd8HedcnvjsTOjKoujvL4QLu2e5I8LOBMzgYUZSMh3fN4Pqtpegpv5VfPIOAbWnHSsk_ghS6O4-f1gRcgp7MaC-NL5Oo3qHF_g-5MFzbLX_AxgwR-5WFJredWHbCrXNRNfZRZMSMo6ZJsNEnqpDOzI2ISXGu61yFBn3qz24JAlr1C6yxobcnoEUnHI5E1fvw7IiyK0Ls11dG8yRRg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2MW1W9k7u8w/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2MW1W9k7u8w/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;美国总统乔·拜登（左）和美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周三在白宫就以色列和哈马斯之间的停火协议发表讲话。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Aaron Schwartz/Sipa&lt;/i&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;周一，加拿大&lt;/strong&gt;向即将上任的特朗普政府提供了一点胡萝卜，承诺购买&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkJRp4qhm54lsEjPjloKTrsJCmhoywcMV6IdkuD_qwsVdClgjlmLK-C7-2TOJ0pHLrdU_mwX5A_5-U-yWepfAxIJBVVGscc7qmvtgQIWEtIokLXgWD-pTZ22aX_guuetoEOI7kNSESjqgLUf8hLIvoejsJLUK8S9_I6I-MehgkYGPBDqvPFoWx1qBD5dt7Z5InSkyO8a3S3loEGkCelEQ1KhxwV-co5j9BzLJjbr08PFS7VK34GOnCSLuZvvn_GpYVqQyDF0wkm6KEWoDE1abkH4vVGnpV7nMb1sOYogzYu65RsQCaO86l7RRxyIZpIs5SFkoLq15D_WFWVvhPff6N1F-mOlLGjHpbizUIPktGMSbwIaNBXMd1P5IzqQgRyuo9cCw1vGBX92WOgJU8shohMaW667c9cmBdgVGA5Y66K1yYj2ES-zTRlNJukXzAqxJWJM4TTXmlBGRx55fnFWIih2s7F-D8NSA4x_zGwuBgb0cmLuifH0iwFx2IcH8vO33Vg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;各种美国商品&lt;/a&gt;以防止贸易战。今天，美国的北方邻国也露出了一根棍子。加拿大已经起草了一份价值 1,500 亿加元（1,050 亿美元）的美国制造产品的初步清单，如果特朗普决定像他威胁的那样对加拿大商品征收关税，加拿大&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkEaRbA5iaqKm89koHiy-xcXbC5L5tQvyxeu2s1_8E8SsqsYS8wp7V79APqC7kFuH-bK8vk5xv-lZHawXbX9IC_Bl-AknSjurk-AZ3Puq-lLRcBESXb-9kwUls-CG-1VPcGAjIAoqNOeD2f7wMiYFjXmLU7sJ58r2PGACJzfmD3IslsDnMBbz1O1DXc6_Bzf8rKFpQ_EWm2726-EG57r3fg2HmysItS-bocK7HwDyArXzZEtJXJExgNY1fTdgYXQ-_knjoADBAnMVQ8ntHCEVzbMtq-37TEeNhQW4kWW1Za8w0H3T_IEG53io9POelO2SMw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将对其征收关税&lt;/a&gt;。据说这份名单只是草案，只有特朗普先采取行动才会生效。加拿大可能会根据美国的行动稍后增加更多关税。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;内特·安德森 (Nate Anderson)&lt;/strong&gt;决定解散&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkKWffM8neEez2ymiGcBMRh4DEhifc5CFz_bmV67rwvGUVtd15lWj2init6e-XZMPmb4czabtoBG9G1P0aCj1MefDUvkD8eBITGkWkSbz3JvH5QNWgbO9IXPUsL_GDT7q4BwgbSLsl4ASo8HsD-9PD8WtZqw6ZcqMKR4ftNEY8lQ1TqlyZD_ASpbq-TEt3I3zzxJvjFGxOl1NI5ciMfRtkVMztWiElFYGboAcm4uQHjCaulDpoUQQU5p3H0sZT2xHweUHvxM-IVA-YM1NAUCnLVZ-DCJc6LAddxAzBdnP8oll2xWlCx3MqnaJbglQh9YIlQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;著名的卖空者&lt;/a&gt;兴登堡研究公司 (Hindenburg Research)，该公司给&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=e7686c6c6bb94fa3a53f8323502be136&amp;amp;_e=O-rp5hBCpYfCMMHDuseHkC6VScFVx3YVvSe3GiQS5HzvpKygCxwgIL3dgz4rv6_FU9e7Us9iNCaJ3dTZBA5v-2_THdaUvO10QVix3WwKObIaXUaLLxgVd7VoDx6tt6wUVqtpf-AF77GHmghkvBP0T9QRRXzvobqVBeL6HpK50saYxkOlQhf8GBZGoTzNF910jhvqEYPPMYAu8TF2ZEGyp0wMGk5PWOV47X3P_Xo5Jlfy5V_PNTJCqxrOzg09Vb_s1GbDWOQ6s7Ccxd-lDbBp2aO-H56lZYCMWFACKhoyEJwMkAoaAXyHhyzUL1a3jFL4tZVToHv3_NKRxLnZT8DJYA%3D%3D" ta