x; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;美国证券交易委员会在一项诉讼中表示，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;埃隆·马斯克在 2022 年提出收购要约之前，由于等待太久才披露自己在该平台不断增加的股份，从而欺骗了&lt;/strong&gt;Twitter 股东&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvr_dXLE1RD4Gl997bSOvsYK3jLNsb_N5jjStvNvKYZL_ZL-ahVlu88DHRuo5970tpYjKrZ6U7GQv8Obo7Zg1A3ELvhSDqcC7y7_QVNvgnFikX_quQ2zOtgQIPDMhiK6-r6OXV4Dl-_W1Ar-977L-uq-ym67FFY22xjpiIbUZMqoBzxiTCKyb_S2XjH1Y_5ctBemRbVyaLDUy25aTYErIt5yrY0BAZrpndy8rcxeUhzmaNWFp_jeJPl7ggZSYm2jSv-OymGbqXlIvF_wztdAe_V1-fjr2xjmyzV9r9jcMBIe9CEWumR2Pp6l2luDbzMCSBQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;超过 1.5 亿美元&lt;/a&gt;。 （ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvs0yqJNGT_rFUGDoH9UIueHg7ReU6KZbpdV7mgA0gUuPtkNt5iGu_JTT4i7t2OlKM10AF7Tv7Sf1FfQcFJ6cbG4YjN_N2ks459FjXiGYs1UiL0rU8btOw3LAPaBwEALddznyF_VKYcmKazU9tLul2wPoSqyNlroQ-TnG2DJ_oaKI46DpsjNsHe0SRWY9kMEZPWcvs9RYgIVpih701h_OR_bq_DquTavlGDhEUVcosLRz8abZ5bnsVbt2ynZxDcZVzneFtJNrTKXxfLdZddGEjpf6UVjEooMkpi3F94Fp6tRCFObbrQeM1E_5kR3dG-EwIA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;自 2022 年以来一直在对他进行调查&lt;/a&gt;。）该投诉立即遭到马斯克律师的质疑，但他还面临&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvhX28Cqg9FpCwvCOf3d4tMgdMR1iQ2OoWqfOTa60DRunT6zrYRfOnzG5fRAjqWTkhymxH1LeQSAZx3XESmCgb-lwHcbRbitTRs8SgdH_U41SqqmCSUvuKObZ-DcPGEXtRoBXjJVLgtsACL3RV_oLaCh_tnuXGHdhJ-ltGnSeWj_bZQ8_WeeciMJn0QmM-9RU2IJPrjypw4Ro1TZNcnvOh49m0nvR3j88TkxPiOtJm276EXw5UXtff4xOgVchDlSNkzzNMMuxuLBMr_bt0XmC1lZbgT_4ONMRvtJLH2Dg1BqXDdI8cHrPfjb1e31IgnfdwQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;投资者诉讼，&lt;/a&gt;指控他隐瞒了对 Twitter 股票的收购。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;据称，美国计划&lt;/strong&gt;出台&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvpJDoMUcl5RDc-3PmM68oAeeasvwXcZr62TcaX0KusyKBLJxAjYZroWzGQcHDRwllF_Rn5vyPFXFHGmGhAAM46SRELOZ0v2zgl8PrVsPI6KP0XaUP1xOtWvPesAwKj1FqEO4hgrhkZpTx0p_4gtmmXqPhp62YryVVC-e_tyktsdOEXa_UPSQ1RngwMd9zG1bOuq5_Hu0iGelqIzgZNJQAB141ze_6_7tR2Irob22tKEKXGS309so8_YSeo8796gWuHqa5lokMBvinsC4aJ4g6OvwICKOIaETgUdkA8ltHWyCWDO-WAZ7_3L9k6M0lGbFoA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;更多法规，阻止&lt;/a&gt;先进芯片销往中国，目标是台积电、三星和英特尔等生产商。这将是拜登政府在任期最后几天采取的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvh4lhOy_4DibFUVxrwb9oBxi3aAnR4INn1hA2vH3ecaLgKacbhuQ3wvzIbaeBYZv1srvTD93zRvCa43Pfef0zVpa9hN6q5ePrCUCp4RKp-0ej1QEq108SWNlJV3V9gkptcEE7ruT9kBfkZVLotVRoOEBXJv4COgQXfwgRaox4uI80yVMZX7IFYzREa4j6qApU19kRAZY3jtgzDsdeOX6n8PhV1kBDD_4xS1ib7nZ0syEw34dW4EKDA9Sh9xKYvoXyaj0aVDa1W8W6eZGr3Dw0WQZ-uWzMYtdEMg9bogWfm-bz2kndyNDijzHfoi3T0AApg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;一系列科技贸易措施&lt;/a&gt;中的最新一项，此前发生了台积电制造的芯片被&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvsqFX2jmmu9q9boSYuzhy5jYoYJul7mCtH6azRaAjHk6TmTTep_8jSVQVjguB8U37MjEnXRhi_joUcOOQUs8H2JV3K0ZKjzfNosxn5rmrsTf5ssyDOfv8kNCnDH-84ne1SIgcLNz05Pc8ZSz5oixWpqM_vXyMx-iHdJ3y5D2gffvj7ox-0gHgewsn0XeyX8ZNSqGYcs59ZX3md6ZQoBiuMo3iVJYH245t6rLdJsSP6eRDGxM49Pkp4tzOhLI9OqkBb_959etUlLpCJecydqN3GC4T-XIz6Piz5Jz9pD7FpLBzS27XUi2LxboZzQRFLaoGw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;秘密转移到黑名单公司&lt;/a&gt;华为的事件。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cell