="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;确认听证&lt;/strong&gt;会今天继续进行，根据准备好的讲话，候任总统挑选的国务卿参议员马可·卢比奥(Marco Rubio)表示&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvp6Fjj7HNdd4zC2JGDOTmL5Qj_Mv3G-VNAVj6rq1JT9ZoLAaI6PQPBxfJ40xoPYeXruajxJkc06Q00H22BplWsgIE78P4459OCC0gO9w73KVvlvraatEsZ4fnu7ZCW_OOez8CxNozKThilxqfsnh6-Is2sxfT0TPhHzjIOpRvnzAAMXzBkKVcjAlozFAh6-Dbd65Dw983CJAkKRC04zveRpHAWAE0_ont-qC8hxLUtFnH_9GnilFrp5JkI7PCCkAJZHlV2qYpyF5-BDCp98exl6jLsj0Kx-t9v2k_eBTz17hTdHRDXtAR2jXCzBwa5tLwg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;，中国通过撒谎和欺骗&lt;/a&gt;以牺牲美国利益为代价来获得超级大国地位。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvvpZWsGSzmTV1x7lB9wkJI6KqqXKp2e2DJBY3MIMUW61EgyFqnE5-dF9Eed2Lz8eUrQQ1i0OFNc8XHnWq5XUFXNxOfKihxOMcovENH1x66w0_kQ2uBn-mUuXbCL9RaJNEVxSoaSe7TAS6f4RnR-ZOBWmxIBzeXMdWdpC56CMj702gnFeuQR38dwT7GzWFhn-tfvykrrTIbgzdwCbXzmAQDa3Vmpng_T6KBA3FoSFbDxh-_BTLEv2RBaIkUuZT26pKBNa2eC2ArUdAgbS6royoElzRr_0_oCeQ2xJLZlYYoPFJDo4oBF7kQUfbeXJ0cgQiw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;帕姆·邦迪 (Pam ​​Bondi)&lt;/a&gt; ，司法部长候选人； &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvjqx2ZSHmgq_Rru-RPzUDFAFBuG7oIXqA2zs6Q3nuKF3ymK9Bnx5AI0ZgGc2WsR2j-MlXfAMvJTYdVXQBllTz8yKojBiq3rasxoixPUIWJ2r1yA6MrueNISMa4v0FZWBH3chHPARc15JU5NV-aL-vMHchYy4XoU-sLGJBhbgxXZG2uaJkjz9tea3TC2EWALDiemLjRxpePYnBqNjElWxOiByrT6M7LcgPoXZu3w9XdI-n5KqcfrVY4NM_CS_AFsBNpt3bySSU4VDLMYAkrAep9UfSC8pq_xHEons0NTeS5iAcXMlQ5xaQhsWRbn8FyRKUg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;克里斯·赖特（Chris Wright）&lt;/a&gt; ，出任能源部长；誓言要减少繁文缛节的未来交通部长&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvisFn9J4cIW-1s98lwK4kfuycoZ8zZ