trong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在加密货币的伟大一年中，&lt;/strong&gt;专注于数字资产的对冲基金也表现出色，这并不奇怪。只是不如元首：比特币。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;根据 Galaxy VisionTrack 提供的数据&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;，2024 年，&lt;/strong&gt;许多加密货币对冲基金&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvs_HPo_oRoR6rHbicqv-2fouVX5OUuqQTvsk5JEkTsH8xl8S5vSLO4T3Yupp0RBjkKZMI19nbCD02Pk9AA72tDDBjEUrkrnn9jiGDve9T_y8apXBNHrE2u079ht4h4-fjsqhTg53DOla7U4THBFGIL9za1K28dZx7VoAZ7I6pc_WwpztWFTyTcQiEUayuiEYToVq3Djh8sq9fcLhzG81X_wjMa-qUg4Zd4jT7RnVF7THSAsbKw3VUC9QNYmvq2Ltb2kdY5MWot5ZpkWJ0c0aGOSrFB2xrkXmsr-6FGB5SxzcE5XnfcNA_kF0IbIo8n6WDQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;取得了两位数的回报&lt;/a&gt;，追踪 130 只加密货币专用对冲基金表现的 VisionTrack 综合指数飙升了 40%。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;但与比特币的涨幅相比，这些涨幅微不足道&lt;/strong&gt;，比特币首次&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvuiKqw_Uk-a6FLcDSF_aLMdNTccRkloWGsWZQ_L6COMMRa9fPcP_nixHAQ2y3n8xNM2m4mOiC9P512Mze844wOkChAwsKK2QrL9yTmvdBN9K_k9kJGduxA9XYmFuuZ-MGBN4xmfz_in5kcWWcwJXNaCeP8pBFHbAA9-33KWMf1SX2KypahDrhJe5eZXhu5EJ4XzcKAOE1DhX5iEVot9yxy4UDpJAa6Ncjs1h4X9OgWOz1ZM61yVcKCSlQQA8s2BicIhDZ-h-0Xl5clHii7IgwxS9B_U1oaoFurnmsyDjkmU7EsnzP1AAhQVVyEpR3X7zIg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;飙升 120%，突破 10 万美元&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; Tread.fi 首席执行官 David Jeong 表示，对于加密货币对冲基金来说，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;超越比特币的表现&lt;/strong&gt;是一项挑战，因为“很难把握这些事情的时间”。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvs_HPo_oRoR6rHbicqv-2forTb89al_i1950k4ue5LwuuAwnVxe_a2Tuq2r09-cRyaIWHB-8ZYS6OFIT9HT0mLxCbnw70FSUx0M3HJiXsH8nLur1PUNpi8OQ4MA1NNuEBUpfSfvE05OVFf9AY4g0HZ2tpFpvuZGStLQ-6AoeHbSLpQixv14W2S22zPfOcjeNeoS48HxSWqRO-AHBv0UQdHNdpnihiAt1bfII2PLNCvAN0IDdZmPypsKQ5Hj1ghhNUmtcq_Yzymc3-uma7IYINCCrBwbahbBY2cqbLXniaQYnCxaU2Rd5opsSINbxQ2NXjg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ia6npYC1Q6iI/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ia6npYC1Q6iI/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;大事&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=cb58ebea848f40dba403676f95b9ed7e&amp;amp;_e=EiGJ3g71kPlT2fBGIGRNvtKd_I6jEYCVsXEJ6CPBWEvGNsCuUx5auKef4pI_tKkfUZNMCMSa-QLTaY726WLYnDVPRK4j0PPLvNYXM_uEd3faBQk4yKSnzycQc8sbjhJtLMCX8UZ0IpR7FpOWg5hL8hIepqJyIMFHwpy5eoWK5ryB7zPWLyV3hwTN_qsLf6SWdG8YrLbNAgzUqEQ1D3gAOnlN0Pb2cFaquszXipl0Vc8FOt_hjvV74rw3wtTV5TZfANxxzSiSGDWWU3pAdX5