因推翻 2020 年大选而受到的起诉。&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Drew Angerer/Getty Images 北美&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;据彭博社看到的一份内部备忘录显示， &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Meta 计划解雇 5%&lt;/strong&gt;的员工——专门针对公司所说的表现&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfosuPzgaie0aHYdoUG01lmejF6zKt0kHYXMTNLzfSoDh8QGVcn9szpTjGlXadNV6o6Au_geImAffrSJ4sqAH9tzF9_kks28_OytUVGBxdAKI07hl5t8vlwIbuXUvIPIStapMP09vS2wwaPvlnJhOZ7ON999KkZ0GS-b4GRFtFpQK8fQlitG-Y40N6RWC_NfAqQVu83fUdANEQQAV4ZHf8BM13w7-3yGOqdHeDxBZ6srSit0i04n0UQvpuHFz6OalG_nP8wYQzhWfY3BJEKVjlL061p7ZdPHHLI3vWQV5uzEPEkKbkEpW6stz6eD-srOBuow%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;最差的员工&lt;/a&gt;——并雇用新人来接替他们的工作。梅塔说，马克·扎克伯格公司的大规模解雇只会影响那些已经在那里工作了足够长的时间进行绩效评估的员工。被解雇的美国员工预计将于 2 月 10 日收到通知。此次解雇是扎克伯格宣布的一系列变化中的最新一起，其中包括解散位于美国的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfosNuzFD5Uuugx-GxWLx3saxhPf2-i4fXwHPnsqkF4CuStdiCdRH0esSa3_hRqxRG9G2enXYxw5G-P7A4zny30yulK0sgOswy8nS6RxXpQ55b92J0TbPvyvaD6bMpI-c0YbW6M78KhT6JQwa3uPqRZu4edTqQOlNlbt1j0Z-2cMxf88--Lly6ZjMrzzKuvb97EdKiuTIHZUwiqsi7mu7XHhiJdEqcKnXjL-c7URPEg_2cxiSZ0p4XtGO7KVg1tDpPSvPSQa8Fi92e-Ir02QCWMQRtwEEHNcky1Zl4zB0LY5DPxJEk80FWbSGWKCbwl7k7wA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;事实核查部门&lt;/a&gt;并结束其多项&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfomtU9ZcqwkI959B4Gn6Gkneu8CXUXTQEkgI48Jd2ADtCdxMULd8YxtHkxzJTQEeAg8u1O90J_NKa1javJeR53Ce1TMOt1vvL47GLaCWni70QCnSUvjZoly65g9egDOCfzSxPfdQUzJGscn6BcBDVgTdHTPb__YCgdLFC7juTiJWsy6gLAPHVAkB67EoRbp-dPLyNfqSvhSQ1TqMv_VI3gXx-ikmO14RLx6hOihX9CmrgQsKpMubaKMlUziCO_3RrEiFEEk-189cgPL3sBUXKzWK8ZXm14CveZUOtvLaRioY82KFVShGz3fiodfKFw1_7Tw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;多元化和包容性努力&lt;/a&gt;。这些举措与他改善与特朗普关系的努力相吻合，他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfopGtcYT_5nHgJjDpz7P3RdFBbwe9Qro_sUQ6-PHGiT0f25Uq9qmA3aFzQTEw3NjNySgYuqcWjcbihM4WCSnm2yPhHJFje7f_yag6py1xR3vV_PXhOBI-IfVcSufIit3A8l7C5g8AVHNDCUVM3a84rrexOgyzAzA6mSGfoMjeVbaWF5zDa-7icSn5mzkOkWawc0BIFqeci_qW54BCSZQc-kNGYNgRSJHEUbT0-X5uOjCqK722wQgm3K4bASpmgZMRqovifHtuc1zRjqVS_GezuJDvtuxf6Zji-c46Hz5waYzuN8JxuvMDbDidf0k3MHV9eA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;计划参加&lt;/a&gt;特朗普即将举行的就职典礼，Meta 为特朗普&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4Fvfosqo0PvlCFFHMIm3xUJPk7Kd4e51WMTu1vFH3kn0VHcio1M0I6qN_yFBTMbWVY_QQMe4_Yz49TR_gT4HPzGdAVhxppWI_kAPe7_7RhM95H55WVDB_X5lELTOj2rTyDLv2_xTPaIbNRYVWhd_0umXK3HNQoFOXbvwHO2C9NqvwPzRwqnbsP18bI78IJh5yGjwSPu7V8QnLCIy6wfnWmA828rywlOBxWbmL2G1W-c46IMND3a4bn2c-ArkmG0XDGCOZ1jQlaUrV-OtXIAX7rlQix7y_HjfxiLkZ8q6xgi7zuDOmPfLL1E2evqPhJfSjn29_g%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;提供了 100 万美元&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table bord