ing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;阿根廷12月份的月度通胀&lt;/strong&gt;继续接近&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfooykNDDpYh37NGJB_91SHUkSatw7fAr7cdUMoK3vT_xPG2fT5-deMnfwQM28W_k4s_Xm5YFsP9FjFxJAi0T84gxsMA3QtpxxCZMYuHC8oy15K-EmjnONblT_PmxdVi5tjmlyyIUFoBeVEcn_71PUfgqZmkPofNCFhirhX7SVyTSpLm6rcxKe0AQAHA5ndt3h0pKxwHpaywESTS1KcPqYykVFAGf3F7kohUdwfJ2E20QNlxfJMhJn22hivDdbk2Z-5_B3kmrIwWf7MJ4O39rq9HmeVNOSQyMA2HvJrQgFB__vtywT8cU13rbVgJ-YswCgQQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;四年来的低点&lt;/a&gt;，为总统哈维尔·米莱(Javier Milei)一年多来首次改变货币政策打开了大门。 12 月份价格较 11 月份上涨 2.7%，连续第三个月低于 3%，与彭博社调查的经济学家的中值预期一致。根据周二公布的政府数据，与一年前相比，通胀率放缓至 117.8%。然而，该国大部分地区&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfopOfzCnnZ0qdvqeNBiNDuS3feqMKvdCIC0wTkkAWOxho1RVPas77dt93X6MLiE1sOgAgZXpmP_VMWasFNRLuQ67ULYly2babL3_DtyPzzSA4WoAykx0igE1tcAqslV0oqTCZo5Xt2R3JdNDekBIrcSBY0xs6q7k3KWrA5vh0fwLIVaK3NBaeZtn1oaesGpBGLDwIS-ArB0XU8NXL5Z2MCQbKRYis3jFqorUUSBprd2zUR03WZup2o5SvKkEyLs4VKRbondAddBXqzffQQ-0reIN9hlp3PfiJBqmgkd4zRDLPLs3kkYMZJZyfnTCTOigcwRnoRXSL8d_ajcFuy49vk_MwXwxLimtEHvSnp5hHV22kSaqxQmQINRwI4b_4MZOPy7MKCKncbEJ8-pR-g43UjehhD75zTe2dDo3aRXFQ5Qjd_TyZSB8c-mhAcJ8qsW7HvkQGRPtK-g6KwQvVIdVb9z7Cspz89EeYMA70ihYK-3ZigagfASfzufFbKdwu4bQ_qw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;仍然面临着严重的&lt;/a&gt;贫困问题。尽管许多阿根廷人对未来的经济表现出乐观态度，但任何货币政策的变化&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfosF_Fg8vet18-9DZ8j0VFDCdoo1mgZVQzmGDoetbEBjN0YpGc2LXoQNyS1tu1rpCJdtWq9VoRE7rmOtxVtj5IeQyR1qBiOLelanA_QsmQ4SsWSmDYt8ZskIICW5GZ_pvxElR09kX-VwZV2i0UAP3IEqwsRRpDHxrj3QNufXg2wQ08XyEkhHTfngRrmqgrcDX3YU3gmkPSmImQkcQvqlgznoOJ7DJ9up3ti_IvjL4JB_0PLwrZtN2vnRnI411dF33w50LjbTeMFDItu9Qlwy1TMKgXbiRV7WsIPV4-tJtaEPsfp8ULSqnsyOFhzyX9uEMUw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;都有可能引发通货膨胀&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;摩根大通任命 Jenn Piepszak&lt;/strong&gt;为新&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfoonnN9F1ZIr0tWsf9CqD2Iv6hPfmXXPy8KlT-sqxp9VzaIHrW--PFxvIsa6Nj_Ki7SZg1_qlJVbAcz-OsJPdgZ9QYiFRgV_x31mfjzBn7I_lXhblk6nf1qSStWhRF8jLrj_f78m2TO0-272bDd6-8P4HqDM0FGm8NmKYUl6A6rHNJ-sR-CY9uDy8ArMmV4LNuBpPHQE4bsvDVplr4HVQ2h2RuAlkF-RMMBH4L_4VJP1lPiKzjfz6FtgIOZGeg7rLlRZs0jhpmFGfdySvh4C1Kfe4g2tRpDGSRjdtvVXU08VapZLuJPJKcP8Yu6x0909BcQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;首席运营官&lt;/a&gt;，这是该银行一年内第二次调整其高层管理人员。虽然 54 岁的皮普扎克 (Piepszak) 从明年年底退休的丹尼尔·平托 (Daniel Pinto) 手中接过二号人物，但她排除了自己成为首席执行官杰米·戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfonUN6iWhBpkvtVbYiASCAlCtFNIrmay0Z7fnzr4KVS2rTmcEkk5hzkLFFi2G_46OoDXvaiFW8djEHN05GPp7Ot1JqB1qSNsSheoI8jhcvuszMPAMxfGHFTMNCfhcGuJdZtyyb7JpC3RrqMilHIJmeRNWvU8ZNivjW8_FlWXZji5frDaePr2yOT1qgNBlIGHULi9f3gPnTOPOk5iVTYIyNWbwZxcxGgSJsDNJS4-SXlBIWAtvPq8izL4eik49owdmlmLmtHXjwxQQeILQ1NwoMhYMYqwruRYyICCnTGaH3IevSS_XOB6YwWAsuyevlhY-vg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;可能继任者的可能性&lt;/a&gt;。皮普扎克的决定是谁将接替美国大型银行首席执行官戴蒙这一长期问题的最新转折。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfoonnN9F1ZIr0tWsf9CqD2ItXYOW5Tl_I7lOH3jF5KAgwK3koO89i0SVW7yygbR_1zt0ItwLLgpCiPTFyTCDG_3pfZxxEEC8d0OFdsbmxz2A2wCrwVRPuzs0UXOnTSCh6RnAH59-zF5BK3LmrfkHBeyCDVmAP5HI2SIfuHdf2AoyOxbo3VQptPPaL-6hxFI2H0C0wXcO-qFSDiDALSDj9lIDrUFsDDCskLXDLxvxRMMntKNR2H8pKVQGVz2Vx-A3BsIrJa3Y3iZaOhXKhqX7jsJ8AcBf19QedBp5OkXRLfvmtPCQOlgTX0KLF8vAPQ_d5Iw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imCGh2X6ug9M/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imCGh2X6ug9M/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt; Jenn Piepszak&lt;i&gt;资料来源：摩根大通公司&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=5aae51c73dbc4a98a2f49741c7c14075&amp;amp;_e=7_WVu21IEXyidN3D4FvfomxpA8O2SVTxw3iE2dmjCYzEZmzWdw9jOhFDrF_w3SwlPsvYVxS1sejJ0v3c9dU-9hP9joy-p0bmfJfUflZtiUKliHgQp9OvOTTgnNbTOy6TlFjj5aff9FeI9XJOX4zLPdEvgfoz2GierJZ-0sqtd8lKRypL6i24DXmlpI